      "text": [
        {
          "text": "All Talk",
          "font": {
            "file": "font.ttf",
            "size": 72,
            "color": "#00BB22"
          },
          "tts": {
            "tts_engine": "eleven",
            "voice": "jsCqWAovK2LkecY7zXl4",
            "speed": 1.0
          }
        },
        {
          "text": "口語片語，意思是「光說不做、只會嘴上講卻沒有行動的人」",
          "font": {
            "file": "font.ttf",
            "size": 72,
            "color": "#00BB22"
          },
          "tts": {
            "tts_engine": "eleven",
            "voice": "jsCqWAovK2LkecY7zXl4",
            "speed": 1.0
          }
        },
        {
          "text": "通常帶有負面意思，用來形容一個人只會空口承諾或誇口，但沒真正去做",
          "font": {
            "file": "font.ttf",
            "size": 72,
            "color": "#00BB22"
          },
          "tts": {
            "tts_engine": "eleven",
            "voice": "jsCqWAovK2LkecY7zXl4",
            "speed": 1.0
          }
        }
      ],
      "bgcolor": "#AABB00",
      "line_spacing": 90
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "mode": "append_center",
      "text": [
        {
          "text": "He says he's going to start a business, but he’s all talk",
          "font": {
            "file": "font.ttf",
            "size": 2,
            "color": "#FF0000"
          },
          "tts": {
            "tts_engine": "eleven",
            "voice": "jsCqWAovK2LkecY7zXl4",
            "speed": 1.0
          }
        },
        {
          "text": "他說要創業，但只是嘴上說說而已",
          "font": {
            "file": "font.ttf",
            "size": 3,
            "color": "#FF0000"
          },
          "tts": {
            "tts_engine": "eleven",
            "voice": "jsCqWAovK2LkecY7zXl4",
            "speed": 1.0
          }
        }
      ],
      "bgcolor": "#AABB00",
      "line_spacing": 200
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "mode": "append_center",
      "text": [
        {
          "text": "Don't believe his promises. He's all talk and no action.",
          "font": {
            "file": "font.ttf",
            "size": 44,
            "color": "#000000"
          },
          "tts": {
            "tts_engine": "eleven",
            "voice": "jsCqWAovK2LkecY7zXl4",
            "speed": 1.0
          }
        },
        {
          "text": "別相信他的承諾，他只是光說不做",
          "font": {
            "file": "font.ttf",
            "size": 99,
            "color": "#0000FF"
          },
          "tts": {
            "tts_engine": "eleven",
            "voice": "jsCqWAovK2LkecY7zXl4",
            "speed": 1.0
          }
        }
      ],
      "bgcolor": "#AABB00",
      "line_spacing": 2
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "mode": "append_center",
      "text": [
        {
          "text": "She claimed she would help, but she turned out to be all talk",
          "font": {
            "file": "font.ttf",
            "size": 72,
            "color": "#00BB22"
          },
          "tts": {
            "tts_engine": "eleven",
            "voice": "jsCqWAovK2LkecY7zXl4",
            "speed": 1.0
          }
        },
        {
          "text": "她說會幫忙，但結果只是說說而已",
          "font": {
            "file": "font.ttf",
